query:
SELECT
                    dataset_id   as "id: _",
                    owner_id     as "owner_id: _",
                    owner_name,
                    dataset_name as name,
                    created_at   as "created_at: _",
                    kind         as "kind: _"
                FROM dataset_entries
                WHERE owner_id = $1
                ORDER BY dataset_name ASC
                LIMIT $2 OFFSET $3
